snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Bloodsail - China Joy (2016) Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: A new game in development has been announced by Ubisoft China, based on the ship mechanics from Black Flag. It is expected to begin beta testing in March 2017. This a game which is expect to release of iOS and Android.
